nodes.text: The DarkStryder Campaign, Deluxe was a boxed set produced by West End Games for Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game. The boxed set contained all four products in the DarkStryder line—the initial boxed set, The DarkStryder Campaign, and the three supplements, The Kathol Outback, the Kathol Rift, and Endgame.
Published in 1998, the Deluxe boxed set was the last product to be released by West End Games for the D6 line.
